title: Moto Morini collabs with AARI to reenter Indian market; to launch 4 vehicles
description: AARI already has partnership with premium Italian motorcycle brand Benelli since 2018 and last month, it announced a collaboration with Hungarian two-wheeler maker Keeway."We are delighted to introduce Moto Morini brand to the Indian motorcyclists. At Adishwar Auto Ride India, one of our key endeavors is to create values through our relationships with our customers," said Vikas Jhabakh, Managing Director of Adishwar Auto Ride India Pvt Ltd.
